---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Grownetics OS — AI Operations for Commercial Cultivation | Coming H2 2026"
  description="The AI operations layer for commercial CEA — connecting environment, people, and decisions into one system that compounds with every grow. Join the waitlist for first access."
  canonical="/os"
  bodyClass="os-page"
>

  <style>
    .os-page {
      --bg:         #2B2C2E;
      --bg-alt:     #252628;
      --surface:    #35373A;
      --text:       #E9E8EE;
      --text-2:     #C4C3CC;
      --text-3:     #9799A6;
      --text-muted: #6B6E78;
      --border:     #3D3F43;
      --green:      #4DB405;
      --gold:       #9A8860;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50%       { opacity: 0; }
    }

    .cursor-blink {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 2px;
      height: 1em;
      background: #4DB405;
      vertical-align: text-bottom;
      margin-left: 2px;
      animation: blink 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .os-input {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(154,136,96,0.2);
      color: #E9E8EE;
      caret-color: #4DB405;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
    }

    .os-input:focus {
      border-color: rgba(77,180,5,0.5);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(77,180,5,0.08);
    }

    .os-input::placeholder {
      color: rgba(151,153,166,0.5);
    }

    .os-input option {
      background: #35373A;
      color: #E9E8EE;
    }
  </style>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const logo = document.querySelector('nav img[alt="Grownetics"]') as HTMLImageElement | null;
      if (logo) logo.src = '/images/logo-white.png';
    });
  </script>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       FULL-PAGE HERO
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section
    class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
    style="background: #2B2C2E;"
    aria-labelledby="os-headline"
  >
    <!-- Graph paper grid -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(154,136,96,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(154,136,96,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 72px 72px;"
    ></div>
    <!-- Green glow -->
    <div
      class="absolute pointer-events-none"
      style="bottom: -150px; left: -150px; width: 700px; height: 700px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(77,180,5,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>
    <!-- Warm glow top right -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 right-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="width: 500px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(154,136,96,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>

    <!-- Catalog header bar -->
    <div
      class="absolute left-0 right-0 z-10"
      style="top: 64px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(154,136,96,0.1); padding: 10px 0;"
    >
      <div class="container flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(154,136,96,0.45);">
          GROWNETICS FIELD CATALOG · VOL. II · RESTRICTED ACCESS
        </span>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(77,180,5,0.55);">
          STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT ◉
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container relative z-10 py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-10">
          <div class="h-px w-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(154,136,96,0.4))"></div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: rgba(154,136,96,0.55);">§ 001 · Coming H2 2026</span>
          <div class="h-px w-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgba(154,136,96,0.4))"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-10">
          <span
            class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1.5 rounded border"
            style="color: rgba(77,180,5,0.85); border-color: rgba(77,180,5,0.25); background: rgba(77,180,5,0.07);"
          >◉ In Development</span>
          <span
            class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1.5 rounded border"
            style="color: rgba(233,232,238,0.3); border-color: rgba(233,232,238,0.1);"
          >Early Access Opening</span>
        </div>

        <h1
          id="os-headline"
          class="font-display font-bold mb-4"
          style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.025em; color: #E9E8EE;"
        >
          Intelligence is coming<br />
          <span style="color: #4DB405;">to the grow room.</span>
          <span class="cursor-blink" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </h1>

        <div class="mt-10 mb-12 text-left max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-5">
          <p style="color: rgba(151,153,166,0.9); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            Grownetics OS is the AI operations layer for commercial cultivation — the thing
            that connects your environment, your people, and your decisions into one system
            that gets smarter with every grow.
          </p>
          <p style="color: rgba(107,110,120,0.9); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            It is not monitoring software. It is not an ERP. It is not another dashboard.
            It is the operating system your facility has been running without.
          </p>
          <p style="color: rgba(107,110,120,0.7); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            We're bringing it to a small group of commercial operators first.
            If that's you, leave your email.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 justify-center">
          <div class="h-px flex-1 max-w-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(154,136,96,0.3))"></div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(154,136,96,0.45);">WAITLIST</span>
          <div class="h-px flex-1 max-w-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgba(154,136,96,0.3))"></div>
        </div>

        <form
          action="https://grownetics.com/forms/os-waitlist"
          method="POST"
          class="max-w-md mx-auto space-y-3"
          aria-label="Join the Grownetics OS waitlist"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="form" value="os-waitlist" />

          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="Work email"
            required
            autocomplete="email"
            class="os-input"
          />

          <select
            name="facility_size"
            class="os-input"
            aria-label="Facility size"
          >
            <option value="">Facility size (canopy sq ft)</option>
            <option value="under-10k">Under 10,000 sq ft</option>
            <option value="10k-50k">10,000 – 50,000 sq ft</option>
            <option value="50k-200k">50,000 – 200,000 sq ft</option>
            <option value="200k-plus">200,000+ sq ft</option>
          </select>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn w-full justify-center py-3.5 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-white"
            style="background: #4DB405; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(77,180,5,0.25);"
          >
            Join the Waitlist → First Access
          </button>
        </form>

        <p class="font-mono text-xs mt-5" style="color: rgba(107,110,120,0.65);">
          No pitch. No timeline promises. When it's ready, you'll be first.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a
            href="/"
            class="font-mono text-xs transition-colors duration-150"
            style="color: rgba(154,136,96,0.45);"
            onmouseover="this.style.color='rgba(154,136,96,0.75)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(154,136,96,0.45)'"
          >
            ← Back to Grownetics
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       § 002 — THREE CAPABILITIES
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section style="background: #252628; padding: 96px 0;" aria-label="Platform capabilities preview">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-14">
        <div class="w-0.5 h-3.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(154,136,96,0.5)"></div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: rgba(154,136,96,0.55);">§ 002 · Three Problems. One Operating System.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          {
            ref: "A",
            name: "Unified Intelligence",
            body: "Query your entire facility history in natural language. Ask what your yield looked like six cycles ago when VPD was in range versus when it wasn't. Get an answer in seconds.",
            icon: "◈",
          },
          {
            ref: "B",
            name: "Predictive Operations",
            body: "Grownetics OS doesn't just report what happened — it anticipates what's about to happen. Catch drift before it costs you a harvest. Act on a recommendation, not a post-mortem.",
            icon: "◎",
          },
          {
            ref: "C",
            name: "Codified Expertise",
            body: "Your best cultivation decisions, captured, referenced, and applied at scale. The knowledge that walks out the door with your head grower — stays.",
            icon: "◇",
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div
            class="p-7 rounded-lg"
            style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);"
          >
            <div class="font-mono text-4xl mb-5" style="color: rgba(77,180,5,0.22);">{item.icon}</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3" style="color: rgba(154,136,96,0.5);">
              Capability · {item.ref}
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #E9E8EE;">{item.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(151,153,166,0.8);">{item.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       § 003 — SECOND WAITLIST CTA
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section
    style="background: #2B2C2E; padding: 96px 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"
    aria-label="Join waitlist"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="height: 400px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom center, rgba(77,180,5,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>

    <div class="container relative z-10 text-center max-w-xl mx-auto">

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <div class="h-px w-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(154,136,96,0.3))"></div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(154,136,96,0.5);">§ 003 · Access</span>
        <div class="h-px w-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgba(154,136,96,0.3))"></div>
      </div>

      <h2
        class="font-display font-bold mb-3"
        style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); color: #E9E8EE; line-height: 1.15;"
      >
        The waitlist is open.<br />
        <span style="color: #4DB405;">Early access is limited.</span>
      </h2>

      <p
        class="font-display italic mb-10"
        style="color: rgba(151,153,166,0.65); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6;"
      >
        Early access facilities will shape how Grownetics OS is built.
        Their data informs the model. Their feedback defines the roadmap.
      </p>

      <form
        action="https://grownetics.com/forms/os-waitlist"
        method="POST"
        class="space-y-3"
        aria-label="Join the Grownetics OS waitlist"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="form" value="os-waitlist-bottom" />
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="Work email"
            required
            autocomplete="email"
            class="os-input flex-1"
          />
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn px-6 py-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-white flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: #4DB405;"
          >
            Join the Waitlist
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>

      <p class="font-mono text-xs mt-5">
        <span style="color: rgba(107,110,120,0.65);">Already have Grownetics hardware? </span>
        <a href="/contact" style="color: rgba(77,180,5,0.7); text-decoration: underline;">
          You're already in line.
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
